  "detailed_description": "<strong>Summary </strong><br>A girl was hospitalized with a head injury in the accident.<br>Her friend comes to the hospital to care for her, but the friend vanishes sometime that night.<br>The girl has to find her missing friend by searching the hospital.<br><br><strong>Features </strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fearful graphics: Monochrome dot graphics will evoke feelings of fear and oddity. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple puzzle: There are several puzzles to solve throughout the game. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multiple Ending: Your choices determine the ending result. There are three endings. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Various Characters: You will interact with variety of inpatients on the 7th floor. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple system: You can play using only screens and item clicks. </li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Summary </strong><br>A girl was hospitalized with a head injury in the accident.<br>Her friend comes to the hospital to care for her, but the friend vanishes sometime that night.<br>The girl has to find her missing friend by searching the hospital.<br><br><strong>Features </strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fearful graphics: Monochrome dot graphics will evoke feelings of fear and oddity. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple puzzle: There are several puzzles to solve throughout the game. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multiple Ending: Your choices determine the ending result. There are three endings. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Various Characters: You will interact with variety of inpatients on the 7th floor. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple system: You can play using only screens and item clicks. </li></ul>",
